# @@File             :  for_each_in
# @@Description      :  Loop over a glob pattern and run a command for each match
# @@Changelog        :  Rename printf_* to __printf_*, ANSI escapes, remove unused functions and variables
# @@TODO             :  Better documentation
# @@Other            :
# @@Resource         :
# @@Terminal App     :  no
# @@sudo/root        :  no
# @@Template         :  bash/system
